ent-CMHeadsetColony = колониальная гарнитура
    .desc = Стандартная гарнитура, используемая колонистами.
ent-RMCHeadsetColonyIcons = colony headset
    .desc = A standard headset used by colonists.
    .suffix = With HUD Icons
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressCLF = CLF headset
    .desc = A special headset used by small groups of trained operatives. Or terrorists.
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressBureau = наушник бюро
    .desc = Элегантный наушник, используемый Бюро Колониальных Маршалов, изготовлен в Солнечной системе. Низкопрофильная и удобная. Никто не превыше закона.
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressBureauDamaged = damaged bureau earpiece
    .desc = A sleek headset used by The Colony Marshal Bureau, crafted in Sol. Low profile and comfortable. No one is above the law. This one is pretty beat up, and seems to be missing a few frequencies.
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressWeYa = корпоративная гарнитура Ве-Я
    .desc = Гарнитура, обычно используемая персоналом корпорации Ве-Я.
    .suffix = WeYa, Colony
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressPMC = гарнитура ЧВК
    .desc = Специальная гарнитура, используемая персоналом корпорации.
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressPMCLeader = { ent-RMCHeadsetDistressPMC }
    .suffix = Leader
    .desc = { ent-RMCHeadsetDistressPMC.desc }
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressPMCDirector = PMC headset
    .desc = A special headset used by corporate personnel.
    .suffix = Director
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressGoon = We-Ya headset
    .desc = A special headset used by corporate personnel.
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressGoonLeader = { ent-RMCHeadsetDistressGoon }
    .suffix = Leader
    .desc = { ent-RMCHeadsetDistressGoon.desc }
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressLawyerWeYa = We-Ya headset
    .desc = A special headset used by corporate personnel.
    .suffix = Director
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressDukes = гарнитура Дюжины Дюка
    .desc = Специальная гарнитура, используемая небольшими группами подготовленных оперативников. Или террористов.
ent-RMCHeadsetDistressDukesLeader = { ent-RMCHeadsetDistressDukes }
    .desc = { ent-RMCHeadsetDistressDukes.desc }
ent-RMCHeadsetForecon = Force Recon headset
    .desc = A headset given to FORECON marines.
    .suffix = Survivor
ent-RMCHeadsetMarineDistress = UNMC headset
    .desc = A standard issue UNMC headset. This one is used by marines on colonial protection duties, and only comes equipped with civilian channels.
ent-RMCHeadsetMARSOC = UNMC SOF headset
    .desc = Issued exclusively to Marine Raiders and members of the UNMC's Force Reconnaissance.
    .suffix = ERT
